OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774436769
OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FThe government is to trial social
OL,7,Fmedia bans and digital curfews in the
OL,8,Fhomes of 300 teenagers in the UK.
OL,10,FThe aim of the pilot is for the
OL,11,Fgovernment to understand more closely
OL,12,Fhow different social media
OL,13,Frestrictions might impact young
OL,14,Fpeople's family life, sleep and
OL,15,Fschoolwork.
OL,17,FIt comes four months after Australia
OL,18,Fbanned under 16s from accessing social
OL,19,Fmedia apps, amid calls from some
OL,20,Fcampaigners and politicians to
OL,21,Fimplement similar measures in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
