OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774436769
OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FOther countries to have made steps
OL,7,Ftowards a ban include France, Spain
OL,8,Fand Denmark.
OL,10,FThe pilot will run alongside the
OL,11,Fdigital wellbeing consultation, which
OL,12,Fwill close on May 26 this year, and
OL,13,Fsee young people from across all four
OL,14,Fnations of the UK assigned to one of
OL,15,Ffour pathways.
OL,17,FOne group of teenagers will have their
OL,18,Faccess to some social media apps taken
OL,19,Faway, effectively mimicking what a
OL,20,Fsocial media ban could look like for
OL,21,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774436769
OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FThe parents of these participants will
OL,7,Fbe instructed on how to use parental
OL,8,Fcontrols to to remove, or entirely
OL,9,Fdisable access, to selected social
OL,10,Fmedia apps.
OL,12,FA second group will have a time
OL,13,Frestriction on the amount of time they
OL,14,Fcan spend on the most popular social
OL,15,Fmedia apps for teenagers, such as
OL,16,FInstagram, TikTok, and Snapchat.
OL,18,FTheir usage will be capped at one hour
OL,19,Feach day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774436769
OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FThirdly, one set of young people will
OL,7,Fhave their access to social media
OL,8,Fblocked by their parents between the
OL,9,Fhours of 9pm to 7am, meaning they are
OL,10,Fonly able to access these apps before
OL,11,Fand after school time.
OL,13,FFinally, a control group will also see
OL,14,Fno change to their usage, in order to
OL,15,Fcompare their experiences.
OL,17,FThe children and parents taking part
OL,18,Fin the experiment will be interviewed
OL,19,Fat the start and end of the scheme
OL,20,Fabout the impact the social media
OL,21,Frestrictions have had on their lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
