OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAs well as answering questions about
OL,12,Fschool, family life and sleep,
OL,13,Fparticipants will also be asked about
OL,14,Fpractical challenges, like how easy it
OL,15,Fwas to set up parental controls and
OL,16,Fwhether the teenagers may have found
OL,17,Fworkarounds to bypass them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
