CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774436769
OL,3,CHundreds of UK teenagers to be banned
OL,4,Cfrom social media as part of pilot
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall said:
OL,7,F"We are determined to give young
OL,8,Fpeople the childhood they deserve and
OL,9,Fto prepare them for the future.
OL,11,F"This is why we are listening to
OL,12,Fparents, children and experts with our
OL,13,Fconsultation, as well as testing
OL,14,Fdifferent options in the real world.
OL,15,FThese pilots will give us the evidence
OL,16,Fwe need to take the next steps,
OL,17,Finformed by the experiences of
OL,18,Ffamilies themselves."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
